# Fortochka server monitor — server list
# Format: NAME IP PORT SNI
#
# NAME: friendly name for alerts
# IP: server public IP
# PORT: VLESS port (usually 443)
# SNI: Reality target domain (for TLS check)
#
# Example:
# oracle-sanjose 163.192.34.235 443 yahoo.com
# scaleway-warsaw 51.x.x.x 443 yahoo.com
# scaleway-paris 51.x.x.x 443 samsung.com
